rules.description: Change caps_lock to control if pressed with other keys, to escape if pressed alone.
Change backslash (\) to option if pressed with other keys, to backslash if pressed alone
Change tab to option if pressed with other keys, to tab if pressed alone
Change return_or_enter to control if pressed with other keys, to return_or_enter if pressed alone
Toggle control center by sending Fn C with Alt Cmd C (similar to toggling dock with Alt Cmd D)
Toggle notification center by sending Fn N with Alt Cmd N (similar to toggling dock with Alt Cmd D)
Toggle menu bar by sending Ctrl F2 with Alt Cmd A (similar to toggling dock with Alt Cmd D)
Toggle status bar by sending Ctrl F8 with Alt Cmd S (similar to toggling dock with Alt Cmd D)
Move focus to active or next window by sending Ctrl F4 with Alt Cmd ` (similar to focusing next window with Cmd `)
Move focus to floating window by sending Ctrl F6 with Alt Cmd F (similar to focusing next window with Cmd `)
Move focus to window toolbar by sending Ctrl F5 with Alt Cmd W (similar to focusing next window with Cmd `)
Move focus to window toolbar by sending Ctrl F5 with Alt Cmd T (similar to focusing next window with Cmd `)
Move focus to dock by sending Ctrl F3 with Alt Cmd D (overwrites the default shortcut which toggles the dock)
